[[Image:Felwood Pin.png|thumb|200px|right|A map showing the location of Felwood on the continent of Westeros.]]
'''Felwood''' is a castle in [[the Stormlands]], the region controlled by [[House Baratheon]] of [[Storm's End]]. The castle is located north-west of Storm's End and south of [[King's Landing]], at the edge of the [[Kingswood]].<ref>[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season1/#!/locations/storms-end/ HBO viewers guide, season 1 map, Storm's End entry]</ref>
sections.In the books: In the ''[[A Song of Ice and Fire]]'' novels, the castle is called Fellwood and is the seat of House Fell.
